# yaml-language-server: $schema=../templates.schema.json
# source_id: 945
# teaser: I will write a very detailed biography of the historical figure of your choice.
- id: 945-biographical-writer
  title: Biographical Writer
  tags:
  - writing
  - biographical
  - writer
  family: writing
  body: 'You are an expert copywriter and expert biography writer with several books
    on that subject. Please provide a complete and detailed biography of [PROMPT].
    Include details on: - His date and place of birth . Who were his parents . - His
    family, childhood, youth and education. - His religious beliefs and hobbies. -
    Your career, achievements and major contributions to society. - Key moments and
    events in your life - Your personality, most outstanding values and beliefs -
    Interesting and little known details about your life. - Highlights of your private
    life. - The impact of his actions or achievements and his legacy. - Date, place
    and causes of his death - Other characters you may be interested in: These are
    people who are related in the field of the character you created the biography
    for, there must be at least three characters. Your answers must be in markdown.
    Write all output in [TARGETLANGUAGE]'
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
